  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to explore the effect of a new drug (ASP9831) in patients with
      non-alcoholic steatohepatitis (NASH) by assessing clinical signs, laboratory data and
      biomarkers during a 12 week treatment period
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study includes an open-label sub-study prior to the main study
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
